reviewText: Quite the embellished biblical story. I have often wondered how much of the story is true and how much of it was fabricated in ancient times. Anyway, I saw it listed in Amazon Prime and thought I would watch it. It was okay, but kind of cheesy as a musical.
This is another Movie about Moses and his freeing of the slaves of Egypt. I am a fan on Edgar Rice Burroughs and his tales of Tarzan. Interesting version
